BEWARE: there is no guarantee that the order of the key/value entries in the file will be maintained (they probably won&#39;t). If you are looking for a `Properties` implementation that will maintain the order, maybe this SO answer will do the trick (UNTESTED!) https://stackoverflow.com/questions/25160293/how-maintain-the-order-of-keys-in-java-properties-file

